item.title: Case Object help
item.dc:creator: @vic_08 Vic_
item.description:
@vic_08 wrote:

WOW are you joking me?

You can only use one case… You can’t have 2 things that have the same case numbers… The server doesn’t know which one to use, so it will use the first one.
